    <p class="text-dark, text-left">
        Perishable Items:
        <br /> $6.00 shipping for purchases under $35
        Free for purchases over $35 or for members
        <br />Perishable Items:
        <br />
        $35.00 shipping for all large items (50lbs+)
        $15.00 shipping of large items for members
        $75.00 shipping for rushed shipping for large items (delivered within 2 business days)
        $35.00 rush shipping of large items for members
        $5.00 shipping for all small non-perishable itemsFree shipping for all small non-perishable items for members
        $15.00 for rushed shipping of small non-perishable items
        $15.00 for rushed shipping for members (no discount)
    </p>
    <h3>Tax Policy</h3>
    <p>
        After you go to pay and put in payment information, 
        tax is calculated and added to your total
    </p>
    <h3>Return Policy</h3>
    <p>
        Return items within 30 days (Will not be accepted after 30 days)
        <br />
        Full refund if returned in good condition or if it was damaged in shipping process
        Small items can be dropped off at anearby CosmosLarge items, call the nearest store 
        and it will be picked up free of charge.
        If item was damaged by customer, discount repair service offeredï¿½If item was damaged 
